  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To study if a one piece body suite (T-balance, Telespro, Finland) is equally effective in
      maintaining peri-operative body temperature as forced air warming, during open low-back
      surgery of medium duration.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
